summary: LETTER FROM M JIM CALLAWAY (TX) OPPOSING  EARLY WARNING REPORT (EWR)REGULATIONS THAT REQUIRED  OVER 500 SMALL TO MEDIUM TRAILER MANUFACTURERS TO SUBMIT QUARTERLY  EARLY WARNING REPORTS TO NHTSA.  THOSE REQUIREMENTS WOULD IMPOSE ECONOMIC HARDSHIP ON SMALL MANUFACTURERS, AND COULD PUT JIM CALLAWAY AND SOME OF HIS COLLEAGUES OUT OF BUSINESS.  *AK
